          "whatWentWrong": "Kaiyangnggg struggled to match the materials to the shadows they formed on the screen."
        }
      ],
      "strategic_advice": "When you see light and shadow diagrams, trace the paths carefully:\n- **Seeing objects** → Light must travel **from the lamp**, bounce **off the object**, and go straight **into the eye**.\n- **Shadow sizes** → The **closer** an object is to the torch, the **bigger** its shadow will be on the screen!",
      "trigger_keywords": [
        "shadow",
        "screen",
        "torch",
        "light rays",
        "see"
